==English==
===Suffix===
{{wikipedia}}
'''--ene'''
#{{chemistry}} an [[unsaturated]] [[hydrocarbon]] having at least one [[double bond]]; an [[alkene]]
#{{chemistry}} an [[aromatic]] hydrocarbon based on [[benzene]]
# a [[polymer]] derived from an alkene
===Usage notes===
*The common name of some other organic compounds also end in "ene"
